  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest medical chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The medical chakra begins to cause your weapon to glow with a soft pink hue. You unleash a single strike that bends, curves and twists around you as if you made multiple strikes at once.</p><p>Make one melee taijutsu attack targeting a creature, depending on the severity of your success, your attack is increasingly more effective.</p><p>● Beat AC by 0~4: Weapon Damage + 2d6 poison damage.<br />● Beat AC by 5~9: Weapon Damage + 4d6 poison damage and 1 rank of envenomed.</p><p>● Beat AC by 10~14: Weapon Damage + 6d6 poison damage and 2 ranks of envenomed.</p><p>● Beat AC by 15+: Weapon Damage + 8d6 poison damage and 3 ranks of envenomed.</p><p></p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
